1. `vec![0u8; max_size]` zero-init of ~24MB output buffer (page faults)
2. `isal::compress_into` creates a new ZStream per call
3. Single `writer.write_all` for entire output

**Incomplete diagnostics**: The debug timing (`GZIPPY_DEBUG=1`) and dispatch
check (1KB micro) didn't print due to stderr redirect bug (fixed in cloud.rs).
Also, test ran OLD code (diagnostics weren't pushed).

